David Pedersen (born May 15, 1986 in &lt;a href="Andenes"&gt;Andenes&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="Vester%C3%A5len"&gt;Vesterålen&lt;/a&gt;) is a Norwegian singer and came in 3rd place on &lt;a href="Idol%20%28Norway%29"&gt;Idol&lt;/a&gt; in 2003. The next year David was asked to join the band Carnival. The band only released one single before disbanding in late 2006.
